        <div class="card card-hover">
          <div class="mb-4 text-4xl">ðŸ”§</div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Infrastructure Design</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">
            AI infrastructure patterns for GPU workloads, model serving, and data processing
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover">
          <div class="mb-4 text-4xl">ðŸ’¾</div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Storage Architecture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">
            Optimized storage systems for AI/ML data patterns and distributed filesystems
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover">
          <div class="mb-4 text-4xl">âš¡</div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">
            Real-world performance characteristics of hardware and architectural decisions
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-hover">
          <div class="mb-4 text-4xl">ðŸ”¬</div>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Experimentation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">
            Hands-on research with GPU optimization, model serving, and cluster computing
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Build -->
  <section class="section border-t border-dark-border">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">What We Build</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-accent-blue">Experiments</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
            <li>â€¢ GPU acceleration and CUDA optimization</li>
            <li>â€¢ Model serving architectures (vLLM, Triton)</li>
            <li>â€¢ Data pipeline design and orchestration</li>
            <li>â€¢ Storage systems and filesystem benchmarking</li>
            <li>â€¢ Virtualization and containerization strategies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

