          <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
            <li>â€¢ System provisioning and configuration management</li>
            <li>â€¢ Monitoring, observability, and alerting</li>
            <li>â€¢ Cluster orchestration and resource scheduling</li>
            <li>â€¢ Network topology and performance tuning</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-accent-green">Tooling</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
            <li>â€¢ Diagnostic and debugging tools</li>
            <li>â€¢ Performance benchmarking suites</li>
