            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-lg border border-dark-border bg-dark-bg p-6">
            <h3 class="mb-3 font-semibold text-accent-green">Hardware-Aware</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">
              Decisions are made in the context of specific physical infrastructure
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-lg border border-dark-border bg-dark-bg p-6">
            <h3 class="mb-3 font-semibold text-accent-purple">Documentation-Heavy</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">
              Writing down what was learned is as important as building the system
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

