        <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Current Status</h2>
        <div class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-accent-green/30 bg-accent-green/10 px-4 py-2">
          <span class="mr-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent-green"></span>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-green">Phase: Foundation</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-8 text-text-secondary">
